<h2 class="bold font-l">Shawn Screws Montreal Again</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
As Shawn Michaels mocks Montreal for screwing Bret Hart, Bret shows up to confront Shawn. Or does he? </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OhCrapFakeout" class='trope-example-link'>"Oh, Crap!" Fakeout</a></p>
</div>
